				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Warrior gets a bad rep because new players go with that job and are still learning the ropes.  So, they have mediocre gear, aren't familiar with how to keep hate, do WS, etc etc.
<br />

<br />
Past 37, you don't see many warriors, due to these misconceptions.  I well equipped warrior can do damage on par to other jobs.  War/Nin isn't such a great tank in my opinion and I also don't think War/Mnk is all that special either.  However, they can deal a lot of damage if played right.  
<br />

<br />
I wouldn't discard warriors so easily.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
